{"tid":1289153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"羅范椒芬：暫緩即係撤回㗎喇 咁仲想點呢？","createTime":"2019-07-06T03:25:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T05:00:32.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"d4ae9be1e954d28df6fd912a7a12cea2faa55677","tid":1289153,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T03:25:07.000Z","msg":"羅范椒芬今早出席港台節目《星期六問責》時指，批評泛民不斷將100萬、200萬的上街數字掛在口邊講是誤導群眾，「香港得700萬人，邊有可能3個人就有1個人行出嚟？」她坦言：「特首都已經作咗一個道歉啦！我都話政治係一個妥協嘅藝術吖嘛！咁暫緩已經講到好明呢，冇可能再會提出嚟㗎喇！其實咪回應咗撤回囉！」她續指特首已經回應，今屆會期不會再提出，相信短期內政府亦不會重提：「暫緩即係撤回㗎喇&hellip;&hellip;咁仲想點呢？」<br />\n被問到是否有官員需要下台，羅范椒芬指在政治問責制下，如有官員自願請辭未嘗不可，但是否有人願意走入政府這個「熱廚房」是個問題。對於7.1衝擊立法會，羅范指看到立會被毀感痛心，希望青年幫助香港向前走，冷靜以合法途徑表達意見。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190706/59794181\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190706%2F59794181&d=5uNkoBKOFFInbKPjzc0vjQexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=8fe9656c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190706%2F59794181&h=4c57d731\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190706/59794181</a>"},{"pid":"5c63efabafb662194670b00cd8fcbe27e7b7ee5e","tid":1289153,"uid":183332,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T03:27:15.000Z","msg":"撤回就撤回啦 暫咩撚野緩"},{"pid":"a4e12bff8865b6baf7c8c6d7bdf4d1a8b33349ae","tid":1289153,"uid":18955,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T03:27:16.000Z","msg":"行埋 = 扑野<br />\n<br />\n咁點解堅決要講行埋而唔講扑野？<br />\n<br />\n如果一樣嘅話<br />\n<br />\n有咩咁難開口？"},{"pid":"9a8fd7f8ae93b142bdebaaf7c49e68bad3d30965","tid":1289153,"uid":52538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T03:29:00.000Z","msg":"你落左台仲講野，仲想點呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b18e5f8e4dbe662cbee7c43e46be75e8d1503081","tid":1289153,"uid"