>\n我學生都識分啦 你堂堂一個專業人士竟然唔識 仲起度9up <br />\n<br />\n我如果係建制派既人都恥與為伍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1b4742ecb6a903e138a58faa71b0cc4bcff110f","tid":1289153,"uid":14737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:14:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>相信短期內政府亦不會重提</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我夠相信你係雞啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁你係咪雞呀臭雞"},{"pid":"dd70cd7f0d5650158667dc2a7fd1c7d9b2157015","tid":1289153,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:43:23.000Z","msg":"黃宏發唔係咁講喎"},{"pid":"6e420d2be41083f6599dee3fc4521dc961e9753d","tid":1289153,"uid":272458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:46:14.000Z","msg":"只有「押後」(postpone)或「撤回」(withdraw)<br />\n只有「押後」(postpone)或「撤回」(withdraw)<br />\n只有「押後」(postpone)或「撤回」(withdraw)<br />\n只有「押後」(postpone)或「撤回」(withdraw)"},{"pid":"906fe370bc197114a098df50103895cfd65cb2b9","tid":1289153,"uid":165012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:48:39.000Z","msg":"香港市民逢一至五都暫緩抗爭㗎啦, 咁仲想點?"},{"pid":"0d15be8a25c10a8bb468ce93979ac4584a38fd4e","tid":1289153,"uid":143321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:58:09.000Z","msg":"林鄭又想在反抗運動氣盛之時用「對話」這種狗招，每一次都唔係為解決件事，而係為了解決你。<br />\n<br />\n喜帖街同居民見面，後殺街；天星皇后碼頭同示威者對話，後殺碼頭而承諾的重置至今無期；雨傘運動同學生對話，後清場，拉的拉告的告坐牢的坐牢。每次，每次，都是為了拖延，消弭民氣，然後就反噬，屍骨無存。這是血的經驗與教訓。"},{"pid":"a2fd110d31ea10f528ac005ee2984daa339bcd42","tid":1289153,"uid":98840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:59:25.000Z","msg":"呢條友冇人性架<br />\n當年教改搞到有兩個教師自殺<br />\n佢公開話&quot;如果係關教改事 點解會得兩個自殺咁少&quot;"},{"pid":"7223ac56cc09822a1ff1f54bd367ab7aabe94d01","tid":1289153,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T05:00:32.000Z","msg":"呢條仆街"}]}